{"_path":"/maps/_ai/safety/safety","_dir":"safety","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"AI Safety","description":"AI 安全研究、风险治理与相关事件","alias":"AI 安全","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"risk"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Risk"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"pdoom-是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"p(doom) 是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"p(doom) 是 AI 安全领域的术语，指「人工智能导致人类灭绝或永久失去能力的概率」（probability of doom）。这个词流行于研究者和决策者之间，反映了行业对技术失控风险的深层焦虑。不同专家的 p(doom) 估计从 1% 到 50% 不等——Jeffrey Hinton 等「深度学习教父」倾向于给出较高数字，而产业界人士往往更低。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"当一个不再受安全约束、全力冲刺的 AI 实验室出现时，这种概率评估会显著上升。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/P(doom)","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"P(doom) - Wikipedia"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.scifuture.org/pdoom-watch-different-experts-probabilities-of-doom/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Different Experts Probabilities of Doom from AI"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"event"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Event"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"xai-安全团队的名存实亡"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"xAI 安全团队的名存实亡"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"马斯克旗下的 xAI 近期经历大规模重组，安全团队被「掏空」——至少 11 名工程师和两名联合创始人离职，重组后的组织架构图中甚至没有安全团队的位置。一位内部人士直言：「安全在 xAI 是一个死掉的组织。」"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在 AI 竞赛白热化的当下，这种「先跑起来再说」的态度正在取代审慎的安全考量，而一位掌控巨额资源的亿万富翁押注「速度压倒一切」，对整个行业来说并非好兆头。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.theverge.com/ai-artificial-intelligence/878761/mass-exodus-at-xai-grok-elon-musk-restructuring","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"What's behind the mass exodus at xAI? - The Verge"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"framework"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Framework"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_ai/framework/saif"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SAIF（安全人工智能框架）"}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"risk","depth":2,"text":"Risk"},{"id":"event","depth":2,"text":"Event"},{"id":"framework","depth":2,"text":"Framework"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:safety:safety.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/safety/safety.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/safety/safety","_extension":"md"}